{
  "stem": "23350.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sure enough, we could hear everybody going down, already being rounded up, going down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't want to come out straight away because of the couple.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I-- if I would have come out there, they would have seen that there is another couple lying there, and they were already hidden.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I knew my sister must've been gone, because I heard everybody walking down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In any case, I wasn't going to be left completely alone up there with this couple.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I started walking down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when I came down, it was like a ghost coming down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very thin, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they looked-- where did I come from-- because they went around with the-- with the torch to see, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did I look a state.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Apparently, you know, in that corner, there were feathers, and my hair was full of-- I looked at myself [INAUDIBLE] dirty, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I came down, and they had one look at me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow or other, they gave me just a push, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I managed to get down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And soon enough, I saw my sister, and we got together, and this is how we went into the trains.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went into these closed trains, which, of course, you heard about, which they packed in so many people, like herrings.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was no air.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The little windows on the top, tiny, little openings on the top.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Dark, you couldn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And how I survived this journey, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The smell, and there were just so many people, and it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "No water, nothing to eat, nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there we were, in this-- this train.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
